# Branching Workflow Rules

## Branch Naming

- Use branch names starting with `feature/`, `fix/`, or `refactor/`

## Workflow Expectations

- Keep work organized in small, logical commits
- Avoid mixing unrelated changes in one commit
- Verify changes before committing
- Do not create WIP commits; use stash instead
